name: Trap Starz Clik
description:
'''Trap Starz Clik''' is a [[rap music|rap]] group from [[Dallas, Texas]], United States, composed of Lil High, Pacman and YT. Two of the Trap Starz Lil High, and Pacman attended [[Nimitz High School (Irving, Texas)]] and both graduated in 2005. While YT attend many Dallas schools, he is from [[(West Dallas, Texas)]]. Their debut album, ''Hood Depot'', was released in February 2008 on Universal Republic Records; its lead-off single, "Get It Big", has charted on the ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' [[Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs]] charts.
